		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You might take interest in purchasing a <a href="http://www.retrousb.com/index.php?productID=133" class="postlink">PowerPak</a>, if it would satisfy you.
<br />
<br />To put a game onto a cart, you would first need to purchase a EPROM/EEPROM programmer which will write to the correct type of ROMs.  I never looked into it myself but I'm sure after this post someone will have already said which ROMs you should be looking to purchase, etc.  You will need <a href="http://www.retrousb.com/index.php?categoryID=85" class="postlink">the correct mapper</a> for the ROMs you want, &amp; you might also take interest in purchasing sockets to solder to the boards so you can put multiple ROMs on the same board w/o desoldering.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
