	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There should be several programs that will check the ROM's header &amp; split the file into 2 or 3 separate files as needed.  (prg, chr, &amp; possibly a separate header file)
<br />
<br />The prg &amp; chr are basically raw binaries, obviously.
<br />
<br />Also, I can pretty much guarantee, that you NEED to know how to use a simple command line interface to use the programs for both splitting the ROM &amp; writing to the EP/EEPROMS.  type cmd.exe into run &amp; get familiar if you haven't already done so! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
